examples.en: She led an unoccupied and purposeless life.
examples.ru: Она вела праздную и бесцельную жизнь.

examples.en: A third of the beds at the hospital were unoccupied.
The unoccupied house started to decay.
About half of the seats were unoccupied when the concert started.
examples.ru: Когда концерт начался, около половины мест были незаняты.
